Firez
Firez must pay for all his crimes. But first the traps he hid behind must be disabled.
#subobj 1
Disable the first obelisk
#subobj 2
Disable the second obelisk
#subobj 3
Switch off third obelisk
#subobj 4
Switch off fourth obelisk
#subobj 5
Kill Firez
The trap has been disabled! Now Firez is within reach, but he's still a dangerous opponent. It is possible that the teleportation bridges in the corners of the throne room and the magical lion statues will help you deal with him. The fate of Jygran rests in your hands!